snippet.title: Redirection Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Redirection is a 3D puzzle game by Daniel Ratcliffe, launching October 24th on PC, Mac and Linux. Add it to your Steam wishlist today:
http://store.steampowered.com/app/305760

For more information, visit:
http://www.redirectiongame.com

For press / media enquiries, visit:
http://www.redirectiongame.com/press

The music used in this trailer is "Space in Time" by Jay Man:
http://www.ourmusicbox.com
